Class ImagingStudy

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.fhir.model.api.BaseElement
      • ca.uhn.fhir.model.api.BaseResource
        • ca.uhn.fhir.model.dstu.resource.ImagingStudy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICompositeElement, IElement, IIdentifiableElement, IResource, ISupportsUndeclaredExtensions

    public class ImagingStudy
extends BaseResource
implements IResource
    HAPI/FHIR ImagingStudy Resource (A set of images produced in single study (one or more series of references images))

    Definition: Manifest of a set of images produced in study. The set of images may include every image in the study, or it may be an incomplete sample, such as a list of key images

    Requirements:

    Profile Definition: http://hl7.org/fhir/profiles/ImagingStudy
